1.0.name: wordpress/best-buy-products-plugin
1.0.description: The Best Buy Products Plugin allows you to automatically display Best Buy products on your WordPress site. Integrated with the Best Buy Affiliate Program, with an affiliate ID you can earn commissions on the products you sell. Simply enter the items you want to display, your Best Buy API key, and the product images will be displayed with a link to the product detail page on BestBuy.com. You'll be eligible to earn commissions on any purchase referral you generate. Additional detail on Best Buy APIs can be found at bbyopen.com/developer
